You and your people can ask him
anything you like. But after that...

247
00:21:28,412 --> 00:21:29,996
...it's my turn.

248
00:21:58,608 --> 00:22:01,152
Oh hey. Hello Angela.

249
00:22:02,821 --> 00:22:06,073
My name's Bruce. Bruce Kenner.
