as long as necessary.

329
00:30:29,369 --> 00:30:33,747
Tom. Find this book.
Get everybody a copy.

330
00:30:34,290 --> 00:30:37,376
- Everybody?
- S. Cooper, she was on TV last night.

331
00:30:37,544 --> 00:30:40,087
- Can I make photocopies?
